#Multi-Key ProbingIn Google APIs, the response from using one API key can differ from another. This is especially true for endpoints hidden behind visibility labels. I made probe_api automatically send the same request using all known API keys. My backend would handle adding the correct key restriction headers and the origin/referer matching logic.
