&lt;p&gt;
Rather than me going Q*bert on you some more, let&#39;s just fire it up.

&lt;div class=&quot;separator&quot; style=&quot;clear: both;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjmVLj9V8HBsyRFnLXfowFnC34gPpWG6SYDWI1yzzKKM5tG071bJ78Lz7qdAXy5KSFy7fSsLOUhOKbcM1jjp1hQIOJyMBF_iJbFxa2vg5J77WZ84KhxnFHQLQZ2sYaFT4mUAoIv7yKbKFeX4Dcb78soX8WddjYOpF1nbN8xaekR2_8ocUUywvNnjEqiurk/s2048/000001.xwd.png&quot; style=&quot;display: block; padding: 1em 0; text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; data-original-height=&quot;1200&quot; data-original-width=&quot;2048&quot; src=&quot;https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjmVLj9V8HBsyRFnLXfowFnC34gPpWG6SYDWI1yzzKKM5tG071bJ78Lz7qdAXy5KSFy7fSsLOUhOKbcM1jjp1hQIOJyMBF_iJbFxa2vg5J77WZ84KhxnFHQLQZ2sYaFT4mUAoIv7yKbKFeX4Dcb78soX8WddjYOpF1nbN8xaekR2_8ocUUywvNnjEqiurk/s320/000001.xwd.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

A big part of the build was GTK3, which is a runtime requirement (it&#39;s invoked with &lt;tt&gt;netsurf-gtk3&lt;/tt&gt;, after all).

&lt;div class=&quot;separator&quot; style=&quot;clear: both;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhqzf7BS2GmyrjCcLQ6iq-Tiaax8OINHrHrUYcc09AcoOSSE9mi3j8PPR02_0A0Y6Di_j5wAqhVfqV9qGqGjhCAlWTPeorW_v3s8J-KBvkyaqzLxXrvuj5V2ywFlCsDWRYB-G8mkJEJrx24FkE9He3ZG4g3ZrvKDcdUZcATLRiihs5Y_sjd9_ueR4HHkx8/s2048/000002.xwd.png&quot; style=&quot;display: block; padding: 1em 0; text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; width=&quot;320&quot; data-original-height=&quot;1200&quot; data-original-width=&quot;2048&quot; src=&quot;https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhqzf7BS2GmyrjCcLQ6iq-Tiaax8OINHrHrUYcc09AcoOSSE9mi3j8PPR02_0A0Y6Di_j5wAqhVfqV9qGqGjhCAlWTPeorW_v3s8J-KBvkyaqzLxXrvuj5V2ywFlCsDWRYB-G8mkJEJrx24FkE9He3ZG4g3ZrvKDcdUZcATLRiihs5Y_sjd9_ueR4HHkx8/s320/000002.xwd.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

